trans-unit.target: Fornece dados para o evento de <see cref="E:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentRename" /> .

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs> provides data about a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentRename> event.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs> fornece dados sobre um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentRename> eventos.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs> object provides the following information:
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs> objeto fornece as seguintes informações:

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.Component%2A> property that references the component being renamed.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.Component%2A> propriedade que referencia o componente que está sendo renomeado.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.OldName%2A> property that indicates the old name of the component.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.OldName%2A> propriedade que indica o nome antigo do componente.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.NewName%2A> property that indicates the new name of the component.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.NewName%2A> propriedade que indica o novo nome do componente.

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates creating a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs>.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir demonstra como criar um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs>.
